Correct Greek and add simple European postal code validators

Updated postal code format of the Republic of Korea (South Korea).

This is in line with announcement 2014-63 by Korea Post. Effective August 1st
2015, the Republic of Korea changed to a 5 digit postal code system.

The full announcement can be found on the website of Korea Post:
http://www.koreapost.go.kr/notice/eview.action?contId=e3010000&agencyCode=kpost&order=regDt%20desc&page=1&pagesize=10&notiIdx=24114
